<div class="wrapper">

    <div class="banner">
        <h2> editing entry from <br>[<%= @entry_date %>] </h2>
    </div>

    <h5>
	    <form action='/entries/<%=@entry.id%>' method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="PATCH">
            <label>first, take a deep inhale and a deep exhale. </label>
                        <br><br>

            if you are feeling overwhelmed, feel free to unload here.
            <br><br>
            this space is for you.
            <br><br>

		    <textarea name="thoughts"><%=@entry.thoughts%></textarea><br><br><br>
            <br><br><br>
            <hr>
            <br><br>
            
            <label>	graces and gifts received during the day </label>
            <br><br>
            (what were some beautiful moments, big & small?)
            <br><br>
                1. <input type="text" name="gratitude1" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude1%>"><br><br><br>
                2. <input type="text" name="gratitude2" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude2%>"><br><br><br>
                3. <input type="text" name="gratitude3" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude3%>"><br><br><br>
                4. <input type="text" name="gratitude4" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude4%>"><br><br><br>
                5. <input type="text" name="gratitude5" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude5%>"><br><br><br>
                6. <input type="text" name="gratitude6" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude6%>"><br><br><br>
                7. <input type="text" name="gratitude7" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude7%>"><br><br><br>
                8. <input type="text" name="gratitude8" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude8%>"><br><br><br>
                9. <input type="text" name="gratitude9" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude9%>"><br><br><br>
                10. <input type="text" name="gratitude10" size="48" value="<%=@entry.gratitude10%>"><br><br><br>
            for each gift, spend a moment to give thanks.
            <br><br><br>
            <hr>
            <br><br>

            <label>	review the day. reflect on the feelings you experienced.</label>
            <br><br>
            what were some of the most unfree moments of the day?
            <br>
            the moments carried away by your fears, resentments, cravings, addictions, anxieties or despairing thoughts? 
            <br><br>
                1. <input type="text" name="reflection1" size="48" value="<%=@entry.reflection1%>"><br><br><br>
                2. <input type="text" name="reflection2" size="48" value="<%=@entry.reflection2%>"><br><br><br>
                3. <input type="text" name="reflection3" size="48" value="<%=@entry.reflection3%>"><br><br><br>
                4. <input type="text" name="reflection4" size="48" value="<%=@entry.reflection4%>"><br><br><br>
                5. <input type="text" name="reflection5" size="48" value="<%=@entry.reflection5%>"><br><br><br>
            ask for healing and forgiveness for the moments of mistakes and/or failures. 
            <br><br><br>
            <hr>
            <br><br>

            <label>resolve, in concrete ways, to live tomorrow well. </label>    
            <br><br>
            what are some small steps you can take?
            <br>
            how do you want tomorrow to be different, or same?
            <br><br>
            1. <input type="text" name="hopes1" size="48" value="<%=@entry.hopes1%>"><br><br><br>
            2. <input type="text" name="hopes2" size="48" value="<%=@entry.hopes2%>"><br><br><br>
            3. <input type="text" name="hopes3" size="48" value="<%=@entry.hopes3%>"><br><br><br>
